title: Kaveh Yaghmaei Discography
description:
Kaveh Yaghmaei Discography

Kaveh is the eldest son of Kurosh(Cyrus) Yaghmaei the Persian guitar legend.
He has a powerful music and today he has broken the lock of Iranian music limits and traditions with "Cold Silence" and have released the best videos of last 3 weeks in PMC Channel.
He&#039;s been shining a bit in Tehran last 4 years in Milad Hall by Live "Scarecrow" show. A really good performance by him encouraged other rockers in Iran to start good working as he was the first hard rocker after 26 years(after Islamic Reolution).

Now you listen to his powerful, strong, polotical, hard and in some cases full-romance musics.

Enjoy !!!
